	Henry Donald was a tall man, a few inches over six feet, well muscled with just a bit around his middle beginning to sag with age. His nose was slightly off where it had been broken in his youth, and his short brown hair was starting to show streaks of gray. He had the scars to prove he'd been digging sewer tunnels most of his life, so the other men respected him and would've listened to him even if the the company hadn't put him in charge.\
	"Hey boss. Over here!" said Luke, his number two. Luke was much thinner and about a half a foot shorter than his boss. "From the sudden air movement after that beam got knocked over, I'd say we just broke through to the catacombs."\
